# Auto-Generated Documentation

**⚠️ Files in this directory are AUTO-GENERATED from `data/section.xml`**

## Do NOT edit these files directly!

Your changes will be overwritten on the next build.

## To update this documentation:

1. **For content changes:** Edit `data/section.xml`
2. **For template changes:** Edit `templates/mdx/section.mdx.hbs`
3. **For examples and best practices:** Create separate manual files

## Manual Enhancement Strategy

To add examples, best practices, or additional content:

### Option 1: Create Companion Files

```
docs/configuration/infrastructure/
├── access.mdx                 # Auto-generated
└── access-examples.mdx        # Manual examples
```

### Option 2: Use Import

In your manual file:

```mdx
---
title: Access Control Guide
---

import GeneratedReference from './access.mdx';

# Access Control Best Practices

[Your manual content here]

## Field Reference

<GeneratedReference />
```

### Option 3: Edit After Generation (Not Recommended)

If you must edit generated files:

1. Make your edits
2. Copy to a safe location before regenerating
3. Manually merge after regeneration

**Better:** Contribute to the XML or template instead!

---

**Generated on:** Every build (`npm run build` or `npm start`)  
**Generator script:** `scripts/generate-section-docs.js`  
**Template:** `templates/mdx/section.mdx.hbs`  
**Source:** `data/section.xml`
